            <div class="two-columns">
                <div class="bullet-points">
                    <ul>
                        <li>You have time to learn to do everything yourself and don't need partners</li>
                        <li>You've already chosen partner companies and resources and everything works perfectly</li>
                        <li>You have better methods, frameworks, and more expertise than we do</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="bullet-points">
                    <ul>
                        <li>Your budget is under €5000</li>
                        <li>You want us to code our designs as well</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
