                    <p class="problem__description">A poorly implemented SaaS product's user interface and experience manifests as increasing customer churn, more support tickets, critical online reviews, and mediocre sales results.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="arrow"></div>
                <div class="col-md-6 solution-content">
                    <h4>Solution</h4>
                    <p class="solution__description">We help conceptualize and design the product so that it makes your competitors look hopelessly outdated and provides users with an experience that makes them willing to pay a higher price for your service than before.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Pricing Section -->
    <section class="pricing" id="hinnat">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section__header">
                <h2 class="section__title">Is our service right for me?</h2>
                <p class="section__subtitle">Check out our pricing</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pricing__grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(min(100%, 350px), 1fr)); gap: var(--spacing-lg);">
                <div class="pricing-card">
                    <h3>Design Consulting</h3>
                    <p class="pricing-card__price" style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: bold;">€110/hour</p>
                    <p class="pricing-card__description">A designer specialized in SaaS companies who helps remove growth barriers through Design Consulting.</p>
